### GET alle Reservierungen (ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Authorization: Basic admin@test.de password
Accept: application/json

### POST Reservierung anlegen – ISO Format (201)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start": "2025-11-03T08:00:00",
  "end": "2025-11-03T10:00:00",
  "personUuid": 801537158039793715,
  "facilityUuid": 801514260581654617
}

###
