### 6) Konflikt: Überschneidung -> muss FEHLER geben (CONFLICT)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Authorization: Basic employee@test.de password
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "personUuid": 801535271508861173,
  "facilityUuid": 801535271739547828,
  "start": "2026-02-02T11:00",
  "end": "2026-02-02T13:00"
}

### POST Reservierung Konflikt – ISO Format (409)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start": "2025-11-03T09:00:00",
  "end": "2025-11-03T11:00:00",
  "personUuid": 800501266110571409,
  "facilityUuid": 800501528380400566
}

###

### POST Reservierung ohne Konflikt – ISO Format (201)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start": "2025-11-03T11:00:00",
  "end": "2025-11-03T12:00:00",
  "personUuid": 800501266110571409,
  "facilityUuid": 800501528380400566
}

### POST Reservierung – unbekannte Person (404)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start": "2026-03-02T08:00:00",
  "end": "2026-03-02T10:00:00",
  "personUuid": 999999,
  "facilityUuid": 800501528380400566
}

